cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper is about a system for real-time interactive analysis of deep learning training, which involves machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and data science (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses the design and implementation of the system, which involves software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, and cs.SE.
